Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙就是這樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The cosmos is all there is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,過去是這樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}or ever was,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,以後還是這樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}or ever will be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,30多年前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}A generation ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,天文學家卡爾·薩根站在這裏\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}the astronomer Carl Sagan stood here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI}1980年 卡爾·薩根在PBS拍攝了紀錄片《卡爾·薩根的宇宙》\n其紀錄片在超過60個國家播出 影響著全世界超過五億人口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,帶領全世界數億人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and launched hundreds of millions of us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,進行了一場歷險\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}on a great adventure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,用科學去探索宇宙的奧秘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}the exploration of the universe revealed by science.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候再次探險了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's time to get going again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這場即將開始的旅行會向我們展示\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're about to begin a journey that will take us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,從最微小的到無窮大的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}from the infinitesimal to the infinite,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,從時間的開始到遙遠的未來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}from the dawn of time to the distant future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會探索不同的世界和星系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We'll explore galaxies and suns and worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在時間和空間的組合中暢遊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}surf the gravity waves of space-time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,接觸生活在火中和冰中的生物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}encounter beings that live in fire and ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,探索永恆不滅的星系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}explore the planets of stars that never die,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解和恆星一樣大的原子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}discover atoms as massive as suns
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,還有比原子還小的宇宙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and universes smaller than atoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:01:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是關於人類的故事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Cosmos is also a story about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是先人們對星空研究的史詩長篇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's the saga of how wandering bands of hunters and gatherers found their way to the stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,眾多英雄共同譜寫的史詩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}one adventure with many heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要想像力來完成這次歷險\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}To make this journey,we'll need imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但僅靠想像力是不夠的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But imagination alone is not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因為大自然的真實樣子是超乎想像的神奇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}because the reality of nature is far more wondrous than anything we can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,使這次的歷險因為幾代研究人員的努力成為可能\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This adventure is made possible by generations of searchers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他們嚴格地堅持一套簡單的規則\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}strictly adhering to a simple set of rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,以試驗和觀察結果檢驗觀點\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}test ideas by experiment and observation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,以通過檢驗的觀點為基礎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}build on those ideas that pass the test,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,摒棄未通過檢驗的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}reject the ones that fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,用證據說話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}follow the evidence wherever it leads
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,並對一切存疑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and question everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,接受這些規則\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Accept these terms,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你的宇宙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and the cosmos is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now come with me.
